<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 09:11:49 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>瑞士外长希望中国能够在乌克兰和谈中“帮助我们”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/swiss-foreign-minister-hopes-china-can-give-us-hand-ukraine-peace-talks-2024-02-07/</link><description>瑞士外交部长伊格纳齐奥·卡西斯周三表示，在瑞士上个月同意主办乌克兰问题全球和平峰会后，他希望中国在乌克兰和平谈判中“帮助我们”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 09:04:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/swiss-foreign-minister-hopes-china-can-give-us-hand-ukraine-peace-talks-2024-02-07/</guid></item><item><title>1月份新能源汽车销量环比下降38.8%，创8月份以来首次下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-new-energy-vehicle-sales-fall-388-jan-mm-first-such-drop-since-aug-2024-02-07/</link><description>行业数据显示，中国新能源汽车销量环比下降38.8%，这是自2023年8月以来的首次下降，尽管特斯拉引领新一轮打折促销，但全球最大汽车市场的需求仍出现下滑。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 08:48:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-new-energy-vehicle-sales-fall-388-jan-mm-first-such-drop-since-aug-2024-02-07/</guid></item><item><title>香港迪士尼乐园内十二人被困过山车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/twelve-trapped-rollercoaster-hong-kong-disneyland-2024-02-07/</link><description>警方和消防部门表示，香港迪士尼乐园的过山车于周三下午停止运行，有十二人被困在过山车上，救援行动仍在继续，并部署了数十名人员到现场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 08:35:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/twelve-trapped-rollercoaster-hong-kong-disneyland-2024-02-07/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查：新兴市场货币短期内将稳步上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/emerging-market-currencies-gain-steadily-near-term-2024-02-07/</link><description>路透对外汇策略师的一项调查发现，随着美联储大幅降息的预期减弱，大多数新兴市场货币兑美元汇率在未来几个月将难以收复今年的损失。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 07:50:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/emerging-market-currencies-gain-steadily-near-term-2024-02-07/</guid></item><item><title>嘉士伯押注中国，昂贵的啤酒实现更高的增长目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/carlsberg-estimates-operating-profit-growth-up-5-2024-2024-02-07/</link><description>丹麦啤酒制造商嘉士伯周三概述了到 2027 年实现增长目标的计划，包括增加其昂贵啤酒的营销支出以及在中国等主要国家的营销支出。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 07:37:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/carlsberg-estimates-operating-profit-growth-up-5-2024-2024-02-07/</guid></item><item><title>IEA表示，到2030年，印度将成为全球最大的石油需求增长动力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/india-be-largest-global-oil-demand-growth-driver-through-2030-iea-2024-02-07/</link><description>国际能源署(IEA)周三表示，预计印度将成为2023年至2030年全球石油需求增长的最大推动力，以微弱优势领先于最大进口国中国。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 07:03:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/india-be-largest-global-oil-demand-growth-driver-through-2030-iea-2024-02-07/</guid></item><item><title>珠宝商潘多拉 (Pandora) 今年迄今销售额“健康”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/pandora-sets-2024-organic-revenue-growth-target-after-strong-run-2024-02-07/</link><description>全球最大的珠宝制造商潘多拉 (Pandora) 周三表示，自今年年初以来，其业绩“健康”，销售额实现高个位数增长，并在强劲表现后宣布了股票回购计划。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 06:51:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/pandora-sets-2024-organic-revenue-growth-target-after-strong-run-2024-02-07/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾将加强在台湾面临的岛屿上的军事存在</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-boost-military-presence-islands-facing-taiwan-2024-02-07/</link><description>菲律宾国防部长已命令军方增加驻扎在台湾附近最北端岛屿的部队数量，以加强马尼拉的领土防御能力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 06:26:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-boost-military-presence-islands-facing-taiwan-2024-02-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国在澳大利亚和新西兰以南设立南极站</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-opens-antarctic-station-south-australia-new-zealand-2024-02-07/</link><description>据官方新华社报道，中国周三启用了罗斯海科学研究站，这是首次在澳大利亚和新西兰以南的南极部分地区的一个前哨站开始运营。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 06:04:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-opens-antarctic-station-south-australia-new-zealand-2024-02-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国视频应用抖音集团首席执行官辞职，在字节跳动担任新职务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-bytedance-says-zhang-nan-resigns-douyin-groups-ceo-2024-02-07/</link><description>TikTok 所有者字节跳动周三表示，张楠已辞去抖音集团首席执行官（该流行短视频平台在中国的姊妹应用程序）的首席执行官职务，同时担任新职务，负责管理字节跳动的视频编辑应用程序。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 05:58:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-bytedance-says-zhang-nan-resigns-douyin-groups-ceo-2024-02-07/</guid></item><item><title>巴布亚新几内亚将在马拉佩访问期间向澳大利亚保证安全关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/png-assures-australia-security-ties-leader-marape-arrives-visit-2024-02-07/</link><description>巴布亚新几内亚总理詹姆斯·马拉佩在周三开始的访问中将寻求向澳大利亚保证密切的安全和历史联系，尽管这个太平洋国家正在促进与中国的贸易。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 05:51:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/png-assures-australia-security-ties-leader-marape-arrives-visit-2024-02-07/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：等待北京市场的实际行动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-02-07/</link><description>韦恩·科尔 (Wayne Cole) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 05:34:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-02-07/</guid></item><item><title>软银有望录得一年多以来首个季度盈利</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/softbank-seen-likely-log-first-quarterly-profit-over-year-2024-02-07/</link><description>日本软银集团预计将在周四公布财报时实现五个季度以来的首次净利润，受益于其上市资产价值的强劲增长。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 05:19:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/softbank-seen-likely-log-first-quarterly-profit-over-year-2024-02-07/</guid></item><item><title>春节肉类销售放缓，北京屠夫情绪低落</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/beijings-butchers-glum-bunch-lunar-new-year-meat-sales-slow-2024-02-07/</link><description>北京最大的食品批发市场新发地的屠夫们无精打采地坐在堆满肉的柜台后面的凳子上，时不时地从智能手机视频中抬起头来招呼几位闲逛在市场农历新年装饰品下的购物者。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 04:38:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/beijings-butchers-glum-bunch-lunar-new-year-meat-sales-slow-2024-02-07/</guid></item><item><title>中国恒大：负债开发商整顿背后的人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-evergrande-people-behind-indebted-developers-overhaul-2024-02-07/</link><description>Alvarez &amp;amp; Marsal 的重组专家将依靠与中国的联系以及复杂的企业重组的记录，试图为房地产巨头恒大设计一个涉及债权人、当局和购房者的结果。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 04:18:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-evergrande-people-behind-indebted-developers-overhaul-2024-02-07/</guid></item></channel></rss>